title: Deeper Sounds Of Nairobi
description: Deeper Sounds of Nairobi and Caffé Mocha are a series of radio podcasts and shows recorded and produced in the beautiful city of Nairobi,Kenya. They are geared toward showcasing African House/Dance music that's stirring up the Kenyan Airwaves and Dancefloors,compiled and mixed by Jack Rooster for your listening pleasure
shortDescription: A snapshot of the Deeper Sounds permeating Nairobi.
